        <p class="bg-slate-900 text-3xl font-light text-white inline p-4 absolute -top-10 centered-axis-x">Good Food = Good Mood</p>
    </div>

    <div class="h-8"></div>
    <div class="mx-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 text-xl font-light leading-7 mb-20">
        <div class="mx-4">
            <p>Wake'up. It's Food O'Clock üçï. Food is something that is universal to all of us and it is what binds us together. So this is an attempt to hunt for the bestest recipes in the world to help crave our taste buds and satisfy our stomach.</p>
